---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="content-inner">
    <h1>For Companies</h1>

    <p>
      CVAMO collaborates with companies and organizations on complex decision
      problems involving data, analytics, and optimization. Our research
      combines advanced analytical methods with practical applications in
      business and industrial environments.
    </p>

    <p>
      We are particularly interested in collaborations where academic research
      and real-world challenges can reinforce each other.
    </p>

    <h2>Areas of expertise</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>data analytics and predictive modelling</li>
      <li>optimization and decision support</li>
      <li>operations and production systems</li>
      <li>pricing and value analytics</li>
      <li>data-driven decision-making in complex environments</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Ways to collaborate</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>joint research projects</li>
      <li>doctoral research in collaboration with industry</li>
      <li>participation in research programs such as Flanders Make</li>
      <li>methodological support for complex analytical problems</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p>
      If you are interested in exploring possible collaboration, we would be
      happy to discuss how CVAMO can contribute to your research or innovation
      challenges.
    </p>

    <p>
      Please visit our <a href="/contact">Contact</a> page to get in touch.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
